      "id": "PopularPost168476",
      "post_content": "@majinara  \nEventually you won't have enough mana to replace all of the draws, add elf mana ramp to support it as well as [Elvish Visionary](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Elvish Visionary)  \n  \nYou can even add [Bearscape](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bearscape) to the combo to utilize the unused cards you discard.  \nGrizzly Fate would also be good because of how easily you could hit threshold with slate of ancestry, but also because of the flashback if you end up discarding it.  \n  ",
